    • 方法详细资料

      • fillQueueForKey

        void fillQueueForKey(String keyName,
                   Queue<E> keyQueue,
                   int numValues)
                     throws IOException
        Method that has to be implemented by implementing classes to fill the Queue.
        参数:
        keyName - Key name
        keyQueue - Queue that needs to be filled
        numValues - number of Values to be added to the queue.
        抛出:
        IOException
